{
  "title": "Virtual Host setup for MAMP",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div style=\"word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; white-space: normal;\">\n<div>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">Steps for creating a virtual host and defining it in MAMP.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">First, create a virtual host on your computer:</span></p>\n<ul style=\"\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">Reference:</span> <a href=\"https://discussions.apple.com/thread/3385891?start=0&amp;tstart=0\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;\">https://discussions.apple.com/thread/3385891?start=0&amp;tstart=0</span></a></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">Open Terminal window, open editor for hosts file</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div><br/></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"\">\n<table style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse;width:577px;\">\n<tr style=\"\">\n<td style=\"border-left:solid #000000 1px;border-right:solid #000000 1px;border-bottom:solid #000000 1px;border-top:solid #000000 1px;vertical-align:top;padding:7px 7px 7px 7px;width:99.8266897746967%;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">sudo nano /etc/hosts</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<div>\n<ul style=\"\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;\">add virtual hosts</span></span></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div><br/></div>\n</div>\n<table style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse;width:577px;\">\n<tr style=\"\">\n<td style=\"border-left:solid #000000 1px;border-right:solid #000000 1px;border-bottom:solid #000000 1px;border-top:solid #000000 1px;vertical-align:top;padding:7px 7px 7px 7px;width:99.8266897746967%;\">\n<div><br/></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">##</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\"># Host Database</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">#</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\"># localhost is used to configure the loopback interface</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\"># when the system is booting.  Do not change this entry.</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">##</span></div>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">127.0.0.1       localhost</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\"><a href=\"http://gitcontentdocs.local\">gitcontentdocs.local</a> <a href=\"http://trilemetry.local\">trilemetry.local</a></span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">255.255.255.255 broadcasthost</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">::1             localhost</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">fe80::1%lo0     localhost</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<div>\n<div>\n<ul style=\"\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;\">Save the file and exit:</span></span> <span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">ctl+O</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">(writeout),</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">enter</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">(save),</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">ctl-X</span> <span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">(exit)</span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">refresh cache</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div><br/></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"\">\n<table style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse;width:577px;\">\n<tr style=\"\">\n<td style=\"border-left:solid #000000 1px;border-right:solid #000000 1px;border-bottom:solid #000000 1px;border-top:solid #000000 1px;vertical-align:top;padding:7px 7px 7px 7px;width:99.8266897746967%;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">dscacheutil -flushcache</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div><br/></div>\n<div>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;\">Next, define the host in MAMP:</span></span></span></p>\n<ul style=\"\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.333333333333332px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Reference</span>:</span> <a href=\"http://sawmac.com/mamp/virtual/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;\">http://sawmac.com/mamp/virtual/</span></a> <span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">and</span> <a href=\"http://danilo.ariadoss.com/how-to-setup-virtual-hosts-mamp-environment/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;vertical-align:baseline;\">http://danilo.ariadoss.com/how-to-setup-virtual-hosts-mamp-environment/</span></a></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">Open config file</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div><br/></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"\">\n<table style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse;width:577px;\">\n<tr style=\"\">\n<td style=\"border-left:solid #000000 1px;border-right:solid #000000 1px;border-bottom:solid #000000 1px;border-top:solid #000000 1px;vertical-align:top;padding:7px 7px 7px 7px;width:99.8266897746967%;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">/Applications/MAMP/conf/apache/httpd.conf</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">in this it points to:</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">/Applications/MAMP/conf/apache/extra/httpd-vhosts.conf</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n<ul style=\"\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">Scroll to bottom - Section 3: Virtual Hosts</span></li>\n</ul>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n<ul style=\"\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">Add virtual host definitions</span><br/>\n<br/></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div>\n<ol style=\"\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;\">Set MAMP Apache server to port 80</span></span></p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;\">in http.conf file, uncomment this line</span></span></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"\">\n<table style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse;width:500px;\">\n<tr style=\"\">\n<td style=\"border-left:solid #000000 1px;border-right:solid #000000 1px;border-bottom:solid #000000 1px;border-top:solid #000000 1px;vertical-align:top;padding:7px 7px 7px 7px;width:99.8%;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\"># Virtual hosts</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">Include /Applications/MAMP/conf/apache/extra/httpd-vhosts.conf</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<div><br/></div>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">   </span></p>\n</div>\n<table style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse;width:645px;\">\n<tr style=\"\">\n<td style=\"border-left:solid #000000 1px;border-right:solid #000000 1px;border-bottom:solid #000000 1px;border-top:solid #000000 1px;vertical-align:top;padding:7px 7px 7px 7px;width:99.84496124031008%;\">\n<div><br/></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">#</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\"># Use name-based virtual hosting.</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">#</span></div>\n<div><br/></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">NameVirtualHost *</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">&lt;VirtualHost *&gt;</span></div>\n<div><br/></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">   </span> <span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">DocumentRoot &quot;/Applications/MAMP/htdocs&quot;</span></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">    ServerName localhost</span></div>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</span></p>\n<br/>\n<div><br/></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">&lt;VirtualHost *&gt;</span></div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">   </span> <span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">DocumentRoot &quot;/Users/jdoktor/Documents/Brightcove/github/BCL-developer-docs/&quot;</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">   </span> <span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">ServerName <a href=\"http://gitdevdocs.local\">gitdevdocs.local</a></span></div>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size:13.333333333333332px;font-family:'Courier New';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<div><br/></div>\n<ul style=\"\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:14.666666666666666px;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;\">Stop and Start MAMP server</span></span><br/>\n<br/></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
  ]
}